opicalization are rational\npoint sets of a scheme theoretic tropicalization. Our approach yields a\ngeneralization to any, possibly nontrivial, valuation $v:k\\to T$ with\nidempotent $T$ and enhances the tropicalization with a schematic structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Aug 2015 18:32:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Oct 2016 15:29:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 2 Apr 2019 09:17:58 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 2 Jun 2022 14:15:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-03"}
