sical norm. We argue that this allows one to exclude them from\nthe state sum in calculations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Aug 2015 18:59:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 May 2016 14:30:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
