rical results show that the performance of our scheme is in par with\nunstructured random sensing matrices and structured Toeplitz and Circulant\nmatrices with random entries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 31 Aug 2015 19:29:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 28 Sep 2015 21:58:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2015 19:05:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-08"}
